function Alarm_trojkat(i)
    local stary_col = gpu.getBackground()
	if i == 1 then
		-- czerwony trójkąt
	  gpu.setBackground(Czarny)
	  gpu.fill(w - 9, 1, 9, 5, " ")
	  gpu.setBackground(Czerwony)
	  gpu.setForeground(Czarny)
	  gpu.fill(w - 5, 1, 1, 1, " ")
	  gpu.fill(w - 6, 2, 3, 1, " ")
	  gpu.fill(w - 7, 3, 5, 1, " ")
	  gpu.fill(w - 8, 4, 7, 1, " ")
	  gpu.fill(w - 9, 5, 9, 1, " ")
		-- Wykrzyknik
	  gpu.fill(w - 5, 2, 1, 1, "|")
	  gpu.fill(w - 5, 3, 1, 1, "|")
	  gpu.fill(w - 5, 4, 1, 1, "o")
	  gpu.setBackground(Czarny)
	  gpu.setForeground(Bialy)
	else
		-- Czyszczenie
	  gpu.setBackground(Czarny)
	  gpu.fill(w - 9, 1, 9, 5, " ")
	end
    gpu.setBackground(stary_col)
end





function wykres(histora_poboru_wykres, akt_war_inp, max_wartosc, szer_min, szer_max, wys_max, wys_min, kal_tlo, kol_ramki, kol1, kol2)
 local stary_col = gpu.getBackground()
 gpu.setBackground(kal_tlo)
  gpu.fill(szer_min, wys_max, szer_max-szer_min, wys_min-wys_max, " ")
 gpu.setBackground(kol_ramki)
  gpu.fill(szer_min, wys_max, 1, wys_min-wys_max, " ")
  gpu.fill(szer_max, wys_max, 1, wys_min-wys_max, " ")
  gpu.fill(szer_min, wys_min, szer_max-szer_min+1, 1, " ")
  gpu.fill(szer_min, wys_max, szer_max-szer_min, 1, " ")
 if histora_poboru_wykres[1] == nil then
  for i = 1, szer_max - szer_min do
    histora_poboru_wykres[i] = 0
  end
 end
 for i = 1, szer_max - szer_min do
   local j = szer_max - szer_min - i
   if j == 1 then
     histora_poboru_wykres[1] = tonumber(akt_war_inp)
   else
     histora_poboru_wykres[j] = histora_poboru_wykres[j-1]
   end
 end
 histora_poboru_wykres[szer_max - szer_min] = not histora_poboru_wykres[szer_max - szer_min]
 for i = szer_min + 1, szer_max - 1 do
   local k = szer_max - i
   if histora_poboru_wykres[szer_max - szer_min] then
     if (k % 2 == 0) then
       gpu.setBackground(kol1)
     else
       gpu.setBackground(kol2)
     end
   else
     if (k % 2 == 0) then
       gpu.setBackground(kol2)
     else
       gpu.setBackground(kol1)
     end
   end
   local pik = math.ceil((tonumber(histora_poboru_wykres[k]) * (wys_min - wys_max - 2) / max_wartosc))
   gpu.fill(i, wys_min - pik + 1, 1, pik-1, " ")
 end
 gpu.setBackground(stary_col)
end





function procent_bez_ramki(procent_naladowania, szer_min, szer_max, wys_max, wys_min, kol_tlo, kol1, kol2, kol3)
  local stary_col = gpu.getBackground()
  local stary_col1 = gpu.getForeground()
  gpu.setBackground(kol_tlo)
  gpu.fill(szer_min, wys_max, szer_max - szer_min + 1, wys_min-wys_max + 1, " ")
  if procent_naladowania > 70 then
    gpu.setBackground(kol1)
  else 
    if procent_naladowania > 30 then
      gpu.setBackground(kol2)
    else
      gpu.setBackground(kol3)
    end
  end
  local szerokosc = math.ceil((szer_max - szer_min + 1) * procent_naladowania / 100 )
  gpu.fill(szer_min, wys_max, szerokosc, wys_min - wys_max + 1, " ")
  term.setCursor(szer_max - string.len(procent_naladowania) - 3, math.ceil((wys_max + wys_min) / 2))
  gpu.setForeground(Czarny)
  term.write(procent_naladowania  ..  " %")
  gpu.setForeground(stary_col1)
  gpu.setBackground(stary_col)
end




function procent_z_ramka(procent_naladowania, szer_min, szer_max, wys_max, wys_min, kol_tlo, kol_ramki, kol1, kol2, kol3)
  local stary_col = gpu.getBackground()
  local stary_col1 = gpu.getForeground()
    gpu.setBackground(kol_ramki)
    gpu.fill(szer_min, wys_max, 1, wys_min-wys_max, " ")
    gpu.fill(szer_max, wys_max, 1, wys_min-wys_max, " ")
    gpu.fill(szer_min, wys_min, szer_max-szer_min+1, 1, " ")
    gpu.fill(szer_min, wys_max, szer_max-szer_min, 1, " ")
  gpu.setBackground(kol_tlo)
  gpu.fill(szer_min + 1, wys_max + 1, szer_max - szer_min - 1, wys_min-2, " ")
  if procent_naladowania > 70 then
    gpu.setBackground(kol1)
  else
    if procent_naladowania > 30 then
      gpu.setBackground(kol2)
    else
      gpu.setBackground(kol3)
    end
  end
  local szerokosc = math.ceil((szer_max - szer_min - 1) * procent_naladowania / 100 )
  gpu.fill(szer_min + 1, wys_max + 1, szerokosc, wys_min - 2, " ")
  gpu.setBackground(kol_ramki)
  gpu.setForeground(Czarny)
  term.setCursor(szer_max - 20 - string.len(procent_naladowania) - 2, wys_max)
  term.write("Baterie naładowane: ")
  term.setCursor(szer_max - string.len(procent_naladowania) - 2, wys_max)
  term.write(procent_naladowania  ..  " %")
  gpu.setForeground(stary_col1)
  gpu.setBackground(stary_col)
end

-- Setup rednet connection
local protocolName = "megaleader_mobfarm"
local mobId = "mob_blaze" -- Change accordingly
rednet.open("top")
rednet.host(protocolName, mobId)

while true do
    local senderId, message, protocol = rednet.receive(protocolName)
    if message == true then
        redstone.setOutput("back", true)
    else
        redstone.setOutput("back", false)
    end
end

title: Computercraft : Mobfarms server
content:
os.loadAPI("touchpoint")

-- Setup rednet connection
local protocolName = "megaleader_mobfarm"
rednet.open("back")

-- Draw buttons
local t = touchpoint.new("top")
t:add("Blaze", nil, 2, 2, 14, 4)
t:add("Enderman", nil, 17, 2, 28, 4)

t:add("Wither sk.", nil, 2, 6, 14, 8)
t:add("Other 1", nil, 17, 6, 28, 8)

t:add("Other 2", nil, 2, 10, 14, 12)
t:add("Pink slime", nil, 17, 10, 28, 12)

t:add("Global", nil, 2, 14, 28, 16)

t:draw()

-- Wait for events
while true do
    local event, mobId = t:handleEvents(os.pullEvent())
    if event == "button_click" then
        t:toggleButton(mobId)
        local receiverMachine = rednet.lookup(protocolName, mobId)

        if receiverMachine == nil then
            print("Machine not found")
            t:toggleButton(mobId)
        else
            print("Toggling machine " ..mobId .."(" .. receiverMachine ..")")
            rednet.send(receiverMachine, t:getActive(mobId), protocolName)
        end
    end
end

from functools import wraps
from string import ascii_letters
from threading import Thread
from time import time
from typing import Any, Callable, Dict, Generator, List, TypeVar

REPEAT_COUNT = 100_000_0
TEST_STR = ascii_letters
THRESHOLD_INDEX = 25

TEST_INT_SEQ = list(range(100))
TEST_INT_TO_CMP = 5

#region utils
T = TypeVar("T")
def timeit(function: Callable[..., T]) -> Callable[..., T]:
    @wraps(function)
    def wrapper(*args: List[Any], **kwargs: Dict[str, Any]) -> T:
        before = time()
        res = function(*args, **kwargs)
        time_took = time() - before

        print(f"took: {time_took:.9f}s ", end = "\n"*2)
        return res
    
    return wrapper

@timeit
def tester(function_to_test: Callable[..., Any], index: int, repeats: int = REPEAT_COUNT) -> None:
    print(f"{index} has been started!")

    for _ in range(repeats):
        function_to_test()

    print(f"{index} finished!")
#endregion

#region upper
def example_1() -> None:
    "naive approach"
    result: List[str] = []
    for char in TEST_STR:
        result.append(char.upper())

    final_result = "".join(result[:THRESHOLD_INDEX])

def example_2() -> None:
    "list comprehension"
    result: List[str] = [char.upper() for char in TEST_STR]
    final_result = "".join(result[:THRESHOLD_INDEX])

def example_3() -> None:
    "generator comprehension and a nice trick"
    result: Generator[str, None, None] = (char.upper() for char in TEST_STR)
    final_result = "".join([next(result) for _ in range(THRESHOLD_INDEX)])

def example_4() -> None:
    "map with generator trick"
    result = map(str.upper, TEST_STR)
    final_result = "".join([next(result) for _ in range(THRESHOLD_INDEX)])
#endregion

#region lt
def example_5() -> None:
    "naive filtering"
    result: List[int] = []
    for number in TEST_INT_SEQ:
        if TEST_INT_TO_CMP < number:
            result.append(number)

    final_result = " ".join([str(elem) for elem in result[:THRESHOLD_INDEX]])

def example_6() -> None:
    "list comprehension filtering with if"
    result: List[int] = [number for number in TEST_INT_SEQ if TEST_INT_TO_CMP < number]
    final_result = " ".join([str(elem) for elem in result[:THRESHOLD_INDEX]])

def example_7() -> None:
    "good old generator"
    result: Generator[int, None, None] = (number for number in TEST_INT_SEQ if TEST_INT_TO_CMP < number)
    final_result = " ".join([str(next(result)) for _ in range(THRESHOLD_INDEX)])

def example_8() -> None:
    "filter magic"
    result = filter(lambda x: TEST_INT_TO_CMP < x, TEST_INT_SEQ)
    final_result = " ".join([str(next(result)) for _ in range(THRESHOLD_INDEX)])
#endregion

#region main
def upper_tests() -> List[Callable[[], None]]:
    return [
        example_1,
        example_2,
        example_3,
        example_4
    ]

def filter_tests() -> List[Callable[[], None]]:
    return [
        example_5,
        example_6,
        example_7,
        example_8
    ]

def main() -> None:
    for get_tests in (upper_tests, filter_tests):
        test_examples = get_tests()
        thread_pool: List[Thread] = []

        for i, test_example in enumerate(test_examples):
            new_thread = Thread(target = tester, args = [test_example, i])
            thread_pool.append(new_thread)

        for thread in thread_pool:
            thread.start()
        
        print("\nPlease wait for all of the mentioned tests are finished then press enter")
        input()

if __name__ == "__main__":
    main()

#endregion

with filtered_news as (
    select
        n.id,
        (substring(n.source_id, 4))::numeric as seq,
        n.news_source
    from 
        news n
    where
        n.received_time > '2023-08-03 00:00:00'
        and n.original_id is null
        and n.news_feed = 'dj'
)
, sequenced_news as (
    select 
        fn.id, 
        fn.seq, 
        fn.news_source,
        fn.seq - lag(fn.seq) over (partition by fn.news_source order by fn.id) as seq_diff
    from 
        filtered_news fn
)
select 
    id, 
    seq, 
    news_source
from 
    sequenced_news
where 
    seq_diff < 0;

from googletrans import Translator
import os
import re
 
# Функция за превод на име от български на английски и форматиране
def translate_and_format_name(bulgarian_name):
    translator = Translator()
    translated = translator.translate(bulgarian_name, src='en', dest='bg')
    translated_text = translated.text.lower().replace(" ", "_")
    translated_text = re.sub(r'[-\s]+', '_', translated_text)
    translated_text = re.sub(r'_+', '_', translated_text)  # Замяна на всички последователни подчертаващи знаци с единичен
    return translated_text
 
# Път до главната папка, в която ще промени имената на директориите
main_directory = input(r'f:movies')
 
# Обхождане на всички директории в главната папка
for dirpath, dirnames, filenames in os.walk(main_directory):
    for dirname in dirnames:
        old_path = os.path.join(dirpath, dirname)
 
        # Проверка дали името на директорията е на български
        if any(c.isalpha() for c in dirname) and not any(c.isalpha() for c in dirname):
            print(f'Прескачане на директорията "{dirname}", тъй като е на английски.')
            continue
 
        new_name_en = translate_and_format_name(dirname)
        new_path = os.path.join(dirpath, new_name_en)
 
        # Проверка дали името вече е преведено и форматирано
        if new_name_en == dirname:
            print(f'Прескачане на директорията "{dirname}", тъй като е вече преведено и форматирано.')
            continue
 
        try:
            os.rename(old_path, new_path)
            print(f'Името на директорията "{dirname}" е успешно променено на "{new_name_en}"')
        except OSError as e:
            print(f'Грешка при промяната на името на директорията "{dirname}": {e}')

content:
from googletrans import Translator
import os
import re

# Функция за превод на име от български на английски и форматиране
def translate_and_format_name(bulgarian_name):
    translator = Translator()
    translated = translator.translate(bulgarian_name, src='en', dest='bg')
    translated_text = translated.text.lower().replace(" ", "_")
    translated_text = re.sub(r'[-\s]+', '_', translated_text)
    translated_text = re.sub(r'_+', '_', translated_text)  # Замяна на всички последователни подчертаващи знаци с единичен
    return translated_textD:\1 A

# Път до главната папка, в която ще променяте имената на директориите
main_directory = input('Въведете пътя до главната папка: ')

# Обхождане на всички директории в главната папка
for dirpath, dirnames, filenames in os.walk(main_directory):
    for dirname in dirnames:
        old_path = os.path.join(dirpath, dirname)

        # Проверка дали името на директорията е на български
        if any(c.isalpha() for c in dirname) and not any(c.isalpha() for c in dirname):
            print(f'Прескачане на директорията "{dirname}", тъй като е на английски.')
            continue

        new_name_en = translate_and_format_name(dirname)
        new_path = os.path.join(dirpath, new_name_en)

        # Проверка дали името вече е преведено и форматирано
        if new_name_en == dirname:
            print(f'Прескачане на директорията "{dirname}", тъй като е вече преведено и форматирано.')
            continue

        try:
            os.rename(old_path, new_path)
            print(f'Името на директорията "{dirname}" е успешно променено на "{new_name_en}"')
        except OSError as e:
            print(f'Грешка при промяната на името на директорията "{dirname}": {e}')

04. Toy Shop
content:
travelPrice = float(input())
puzzles = int(input())
dolls = int(input())
bears = int(input())
minions = int(input())
lorries = int(input())

puzzlesPrice = 2.6
dollsPrice = 3.0
bearsPrice = 4.1
minionsPrice = 8.20
lorriesPrice = 2.0

puzzlesValue = puzzlesPrice * puzzles
dollsValue = dollsPrice * dolls
bearsValue = bearsPrice * bears
minionsValue = minionsPrice * minions
lorriesValue = lorriesPrice * lorries

toys = puzzles + dolls + bears + minions + lorries
toysValue = puzzlesValue + dollsValue + bearsValue + minionsValue + lorriesValue

if toys >= 50:
    toysValue = 0.75 * toysValue

profit = toysValue * 0.9

if profit >= travelPrice:
    print(f"Yes! {profit - travelPrice:.2f} lv left.")
else:
    print(f"Not enough money! {travelPrice - profit:.2f} lv needed.")

Удаление дубликатов файлов по хеш функции
content:
import os
from tkinter import Tk
from hashlib import md5
from pathlib import Path
from colorama import init, Fore
from tkinter.filedialog import askdirectory

init()
Tk().withdraw()
file_path = askdirectory(title="Каталог для удаления дубликатов")
list_of_files = os.walk(file_path)
unique_files = dict()
number = 1

for root, folders, files in list_of_files:
    for file in files:
        file_path = Path(os.path.join(root, file))
        Hash_file = md5(open(file_path, 'rb').read()).hexdigest()
        if Hash_file not in unique_files:
            unique_files[Hash_file] = file_path
            print(Fore.GREEN + "[%i] %s %s" % (number, Hash_file, file_path))
        else:
            os.remove(file_path)
            print(Fore.RED + "[%i] %s %s" % (number, Hash_file, file_path))
        number += 1

title: Get-ImprivataADReport
content:
# Requires -Module ImportExcel

[Flags()] enum UAC {
    SCRIPT                         = 1
    ACCOUNTDISABLE                 = 2
    HOMEDIR_REQUIRED               = 8
    LOCKOUT                        = 16
    PASSWD_NOTREQD                 = 32
    PASSWD_CANT_CHANGE             = 64
    ENCRYPTED_TEXT_PWD_ALLOWED     = 128
    TEMP_DUPLICATE_ACCOUNT         = 256
    NORMAL_ACCOUNT                 = 512
    INTERDOMAIN_TRUST_ACCOUNT      = 2048
    WORKSTATION_TRUST_ACCOUNT      = 4096
    SERVER_TRUST_ACCOUNT           = 8192
    DONT_EXPIRE_PASSWORD           = 65536
    MNS_LOGON_ACCOUNT              = 131072
    SMARTCARD_REQUIRED             = 262144
    TRUSTED_FOR_DELEGATION         = 524288
    NOT_DELEGATED                  = 1048576
    USE_DES_KEY_ONLY               = 2097152
    DONT_REQ_PREAUTH               = 4194304
    PASSWORD_EXPIRED               = 8388608
    TRUSTED_TO_AUTH_FOR_DELEGATION = 16777216
    PARTIAL_SECRETS_ACCOUNT        = 67108864
}
 
function Get-ImprivataADReport {
    <#
    .SYNOPSIS
        This is a script to take an im
    .DESCRIPTION
        A longer description of the function, its purpose, common use cases, etc.
    .NOTES
        Information or caveats about the function e.g. 'This function is not supported in Linux'
    .LINK
        Specify a URI to a help page, this will show when Get-Help -Online is used.
    .EXAMPLE
        Test-MyTestFunction -Verbose
        Explanation of the function or its result. You can include multiple examples with additional .EXAMPLE lines
    #>
    param(
        [parameter(Mandatory, ValueFromPipelineByPropertyName)]
        [ValidateScript({
            Test-Path -Path $_
        })]
        [string]$InputCSV,
 
        [parameter(ValueFromPipelineByPropertyName)]
        [string]$Delimiter = ',',
 
        [parameter(Mandatory, ValueFromPipelineByPropertyName)]
        [string]$OutputFile,
 
        [parameter(ValueFromPipelineByPropertyName)]
        [string]$WorkSheetName = 'Providers',
 
        [parameter(ValueFromPipelineByPropertyName)]
        [string[]]$InputPropertyList = ('department', 'title', 'company', 'description','userAccountControl'),
 
        [parameter(ValueFromPipelineByPropertyName)]
        [int]$FlushCounter = 50,
 
        [parameter(ValueFromPipelineByPropertyName)]
        [switch]$ShowProgress
    )
 
    $ExportProperties = @{
        Path            = $OutputFile
        WorksheetName   = $WorkSheetName
        AutoSize        = $true
        Append          = $true
        FreezeTopRow    = $true
        AutoFilter      = $true
        BoldTopRow      = $true
    }
  
    $ADSISearcher               = [adsisearcher]::new()
    $ADSISearcher.SearchRoot    = 'LDAP://OU=Non-Privileged,OU=Accounts,OU=HCHD,DC=hchd,DC=local'
    foreach ($property in $InputPropertyList) {
        [void]($ADSISearcher.PropertiesToLoad.Add($property) )
    }
 
    $csv            = Import-CSV -Path $InputCSV -Delimiter $Delimiter
    $Output         = [System.Collections.Generic.List[pscustomobject]]::new()

    $ProgressCounter = 0

    foreach ($record in $csv) {
        if ($ShowProgress) {
            $ProgressCounter++
            if ($ProgressCounter % $FlushCounter -eq 0) {
                $ProgressParameters = @{
                    Activity            = 'Retrieving AD information from Imprivata Report ({0} of {1})' -f $ProgressCounter, $csv.Count
                    CurrentOperation    = $record.User
                    PercentComplete     = [int]($ProgressCounter/$csv.Count * 100)
                }
                Write-Progress @ProgressParameters
            }
        }

        $ADSISearcher.Filter    =  '(&(objectClass=User)(samaccountname={0}))' -f $record.user
        $thisUser               = $ADSISearcher.findone()
        Write-Verbose -Message ('Processing user: {0}; {1} of {2}' -f $record.User, $ProgressCounter, $csv.count)

        $PropertyMap = [ordered]@{
            user            = $record.User
            FirstName       = $record.'First Name'
            LastName        = $record.'Last Name'
            Domain          = $record.Domain
            UserStatus      = $record.'User Status'
            Enrollment      = $record.'Confirm ID(MFA) Enrolled'
            PolicyName      = $record.'Policy Name'
            Department      = $thisUser.Properties.department | Select-Object -First 1
            JobTitle        = $thisUser.Properties.title | Select-Object -First 1
            Affiliation     = $thisUser.Properties.company | Select-Object -First 1
            ProviderID      = [string]$thisUser.Properties.description | Select-Object -First 1
            AccountEnabled  = -not [bool]($thisUser.Properties.useraccountcontrol -as [UAC]).HasFlag([UAC]::ACCOUNTDISABLE)
        }

        $Output.Add([pscustomobject]$PropertyMap)

        if ($Output.Count % $FlushCounter -eq 0) {
            $Message = 'Exporting and flushing current records; FlushCounter is set to {0}' -f $FlushCounter
            Write-Verbose -Message $Message
            $Output | Export-Excel @ExportProperties
            $Output.Clear()
        }
    }
    $Output | Export-Excel @ExportProperties
    Write-Verbose -Message 'Report Completed' -Verbose
}
